### v03 — Deeper Game Flow (straddle + ante_override + run_it_twice 회귀)
###
### S9 Cycle 7 신규 시나리오 (2026-05-12, issue #328).
### 본 시나리오는 v02 의 multi-hand state transition 위에 Cycle 6 v03 룰 3종 회귀를 추가한다.
###
### 의존성:
###   - S8 Cycle 6 PR #319 (issue #310) — Multi_Hand_v03 룰 머지 완료
###     코드: team3-engine/lib/engine.dart::_handleManualNextHandFull (straddle 회전)
###     코드: team3-engine/lib/engine.dart::_handleAnteOverrideFull (신규)
###     코드: team3-engine/lib/engine.dart::_handleRunItChoiceFull (분할 pot)
###     코드: team3-engine/lib/harness/server.dart::_addEvent (ante_override / run_it_choice routing)
###     코드: team3-engine/lib/harness/server.dart::_nextHand (response.runItBoard2Cards key 추가)
###     테스트: team3-engine/test/multi_hand_v03_test.dart (18 cases ALL PASS)
###     테스트: team3-engine/test/harness/next_hand_v03_endpoint_test.dart (3 cases ALL PASS)
###     스펙: docs/2. Development/2.3 Game Engine/Rules/Multi_Hand_v03.md (contract tier)
###   - S9 Cycle 6 PR #320 (issue #311) — v02 multi-hand e2e baseline
###
### Pipeline (9 phase):
###   Phase A — Setup (health, variants)
###   Phase B — Straddle session + /next-hand straddleSeat 회전 검증 [v03 KEY #1]
###   Phase C — AnteOverride 이벤트 + /next-hand anteAmount 영속화 검증 [v03 KEY #2]
###   Phase D — RunItChoice 이벤트 routing + runItBoard2Cards key shape 검증 [v03 KEY #3]
###   Phase E — Combined straddle + ante 동시 활성 회귀
###   Phase F — v01 baseline 회귀 (fold-to-BB 1-hand)
###   Phase G — v02 baseline 회귀 (POST /next-hand rotation)
###   Phase H — v03 4-hand round-robin straddle wrap-around
###   Phase I — Final DoD cumulative
###
### Coverage:
###   - Multi_Hand_v03.md §1 straddle_seat 회전 (6-seat round-robin)
###   - Multi_Hand_v03.md §2 ante_override 영속성 (다음 hand 까지 유지)
###   - Multi_Hand_v03.md §3 run_it_twice routing (helper 호환 — pre-river 시 runItBoard2Cards=null)
###   - Multi_Hand_v03.md §4 next-hand response 신규 필드 (sbSeat / bbSeat / runItBoard2Cards)
###   - Cycle 5 issue #287 (v02 /next-hand) 회귀 보장
###   - Cycle 4 issue #248 (v01 1-hand flow) 회귀 보장
###
### 실행 검증: 2026-05-12 S9 Cycle 7 — Engine harness :18080 직결.
### Evidence: integration-tests/evidence/cycle7-2026-05-12/v03-deeper-game/

@engine = http://localhost:18080

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase A: Setup — Engine 가동 확인 (v01/v02 동일 baseline)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### A.1 GET /health — Engine harness 가동 확인
GET {{engine}}/health

# Assertion:
#   - status === 200
#   - body.status === "ok"
#   - body.service === "ebs-game-engine"

### A.2 GET /api/variants — variant registry 회귀 (nlh 포함)
GET {{engine}}/api/variants

# Assertion:
#   - status === 200
#   - variants includes "nlh"

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase B: Straddle session — straddleSeat 회전 (v03 KEY #1)
#
# config.straddleEnabled=true, straddleSeat=3 으로 6-seat 세션 생성.
# POST /next-hand 시 dealer 0→1 회전과 함께 straddleSeat 3→4 회전 검증.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### B.1 POST /api/session — straddle 활성 6-seat 세션
# @name straddleSession
POST {{engine}}/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant": "nlh",
  "seatCount": 6,
  "config": {
    "straddleEnabled": true,
    "straddleSeat": 3
  }
}

# Assertion (Phase B.1):
#   - status === 201
#   - sessionId matches /^[a-z0-9]+$/
#   - straddleEnabled === true (v03 NEW field in toJson)
#   - straddleSeat === 3
#   - handNumber === 0
#   - dealerSeat === 0

### B.2 POST /next-hand — straddleSeat 1칸 회전 [v03 KEY]
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{straddleSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion (Multi_Hand_v03.md §1.4):
#   - status === 200
#   - handNumber === 1 (0 → 1)
#   - dealerSeat === 1 (0 → 1)
#   - sbSeat === 2 (dealer+1, v03 NEW key)
#   - bbSeat === 3 (dealer+2, v03 NEW key)
#   - straddleEnabled === true
#   - straddleSeat === 4 (3 → 4, 1칸 회전)
#   - runItBoard2Cards === null (RIT 미발동)

### B.3 POST /next-hand — straddle round-robin 2회차
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{straddleSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 2
#   - dealerSeat === 2 (1 → 2)
#   - straddleSeat === 5 (4 → 5)
#   - sbSeat === 3, bbSeat === 4

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase C: AnteOverride — anteAmount 영속화 (v03 KEY #2)
#
# 새 세션 생성 후 ante_override 이벤트 dispatch.
# /next-hand 진행 시 anteAmount 가 override 값으로 유지되는지 검증.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### C.1 POST /api/session — vanilla 6-seat 세션 (ante 미설정)
# @name anteSession
POST {{engine}}/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant": "nlh",
  "seatCount": 6
}

# Assertion:
#   - status === 201
#   - anteAmount === null (또는 0)

### C.2 POST event — ante_override (amount=100, anteType=2 BB Ante)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{anteSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ante_override",
  "amount": 100,
  "anteType": 2
}

# Assertion (Multi_Hand_v03.md §2.3):
#   - status === 200
#   - anteAmount === 100
#   - anteType === 2

### C.3 POST /next-hand — anteAmount 100 유지 검증 (Multi_Hand_v03.md §2.2)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{anteSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - status === 200
#   - handNumber === 1
#   - anteAmount === 100 (override 영구 유지)
#   - anteType === 2

### C.4 POST event — ante_override 재갱신 (amount=200)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{anteSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ante_override",
  "amount": 200
}

# Assertion:
#   - anteAmount === 200 (재override)
#   - anteType === 2 (이전 값 유지 — type 미지정)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase D: RunItChoice routing — runItBoard2Cards key shape (v03 KEY #3)
#
# run_it_choice 이벤트가 harness 에서 정상 routing 되는지 검증.
# Pre-river 상태에서는 runItBoard2Cards=null (Multi_Hand_v03.md §3.1
# "river 이후 (community.length == 5) 에 RunItChoice 가 dispatch 되면" 조건).
# 본 phase 는 event 수용성 + response field shape 검증 (helper 정합).
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### D.1 POST /api/session — 신규 vanilla 세션
# @name ritSession
POST {{engine}}/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant": "nlh",
  "seatCount": 6
}

# Assertion:
#   - status === 201
#   - runItTimes === null (또는 미포함)
#   - runItBoard2Cards === null (또는 미포함)

### D.2 POST event — run_it_choice (times=2)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{ritSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "run_it_choice",
  "times": 2
}

# Assertion (Multi_Hand_v03.md §3 — graceful pre-river):
#   - status === 200 (event 정상 수용, "Unknown event type" 400 금지)
#   - runItBoard2Cards key present (값은 null — pre-river)
#
# Note: 실 RIT 분할 pot 산출은 community.length==5 + 2+ all-in 상태 필요.
#       본 phase 는 routing + response shape 검증만 (단위 테스트 multi_hand_v03_test.dart
#       에서 분할 로직 18 cases ALL PASS 보장).

### D.3 POST /next-hand — RIT 미적용 시 runItBoard2Cards 유지
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{ritSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 1
#   - runItBoard2Cards === null

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase E: Combined straddle + ante 동시 활성
#
# straddle + ante 가 같은 세션에서 독립적으로 작동하는지 검증.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### E.1 POST /api/session — straddle + ante 동시 활성
# @name combinedSession
POST {{engine}}/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant": "nlh",
  "seatCount": 6,
  "config": {
    "straddleEnabled": true,
    "straddleSeat": 4,
    "anteType": 0,
    "anteAmount": 5
  }
}

# Assertion:
#   - status === 201
#   - straddleEnabled === true
#   - straddleSeat === 4
#   - anteAmount === 5
#   - anteType === 0 (Standard Ante)
#   - pot.main > 15 (SB 5 + BB 10 + 6×ante 5 = 45) — ante 정상 처리

### E.2 POST event — ante_override 중간 변경
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{combinedSession.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ante_override",
  "amount": 50
}

# Assertion:
#   - anteAmount === 50
#   - straddleSeat === 4 (straddle 미영향)

### E.3 POST /next-hand — straddle 회전 + ante 유지 동시 검증
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{combinedSession.response.body.sessionId}}/next-hand

# Assertion:
#   - handNumber === 1
#   - dealerSeat === 1
#   - straddleSeat === 5 (4 → 5)
#   - anteAmount === 50 (override 영구 유지)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
