POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{v01Regression.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{ "type": "fold", "seatIndex": 0 }

### F.6 POST event — fold SB seat 1
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{v01Regression.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{ "type": "fold", "seatIndex": 1 }

### F.7 POST event — pot_awarded to BB (idx 2)
POST {{engine}}/api/session/{{v01Regression.response.body.sessionId}}/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "pot_awarded",
  "awards": { "2": 15 }
}

# Assertion (v01 동일):
