GET {{engine}}/api/session/{{combinedSession.response.body.sessionId}}

# DoD Assertion (Phase E 누적):
#   - straddleSeat === 5
#   - anteAmount === 50
#   - handNumber === 1

### I.4 GET — round-robin session 최종 상태 검증
GET {{engine}}/api/session/{{roundRobinSession.response.body.sessionId}}

# DoD Assertion (Phase H 누적 — wrap-around 검증):
#   - handNumber === 4
#   - dealerSeat === 4
#   - straddleSeat === 1

### I.5 GET — v01 regression session 최종 상태
GET {{engine}}/api/session/{{v01Regression.response.body.sessionId}}

# DoD Assertion (Phase F+G 누적):
#   - handNumber === 2
