# - [x] RunItChoice routing: event 정상 수용 (400 금지) + runItBoard2Cards key
# - [x] Combined straddle + ante 독립 작동 (서로 간섭 없음)
# - [x] v01 baseline 회귀 (fold-to-BB, pot_award)
# - [x] v02 baseline 회귀 (/next-hand rotation, folded→active 복귀)
# - [x] /next-hand response 신규 필드 (sbSeat / bbSeat / runItBoard2Cards) 존재
